title: Disturbed - Indestructible 2008 FLAC
description:
This is Disturbed&#039;s latest album Indestructible.

Retail version copied in FLAC under secure mode, plus a cue sheet.

This image is designed to be burned and the FLAC file needs to be decompressed to burn it to a CD.

The people at the RIAA, my ass. Disturbed doesn&#039;t need your protection and never asked for it. Go ask Draiman about it while the RIAA strips off money from their hard work.

Now, if you like it. Don&#039;t buy the CD, but go to their live concert instead. You&#039;re supporting them directly instead of supporting the RIAA&#039;s witch hunt for P2P.
